OL,10,G1700FFour in a Bed
OL,11,     GThe new run continues. The week's
OL,12,     Gfinal visit is to Jordan and
OL,13,     GRobin's pub in Somerset. But with
OL,14,     Gone B&Ber dreading the potential
OL,15,     Gof stale ale smell, the hosts
OL,16,     Ghave their work cut out.
