OL,11,G1700F5 News at 5
OL,12,G1800FLove Nature
OL,13,     GThe greater horseshoe bat was
OL,14,     Gonce widespread in the UK but due
OL,15,     Gto habitat loss their numbers
OL,16,     Gplummeted. The Vincent Wildlife
OL,17,     GTrust look after around 50% of
OL,18,     Gthe UK's population.
